        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-07-12 15:11:11.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 13: Code-Review-1\n\nYour most recent change has reverted to only modifying the current jobs and not taking care of all the templates and other calls.\n\nGiven that we're just trying to step through to getting transitioned to global-jjb I'm going to suggest that you modify the two JJB jobs so that they don't call the scm macro but fully define the scm section instead locally. That way you can add in the needed recursive call on just them.",
